Infinite Gaussian Mixture Model

Details:

* Dirichlet Process (Stick-Breaking Representation)

* Variational EM (Truncate variational distribution)

Reference:

Variational Inference for Dirichlet Process Mixtures

David M. Blei, Michael I. Jordan

Bayesian Analysis (2006)

http://www.cs.princeton.edu/~blei/papers/BleiJordan2004.pdf

Jacob's matlab library for Gaussian Dirichlet Process Mixture Models (DPMMs).

Jacob Eisenstein

2012

https://github.com/jacobeisenstein/DPMM/tree/master/vdpmm

Note that the variable names are followed from Blei's paper

